Sitting in a box weigh eight pounds but take up a full-size bed or lick the curtain just to be annoying yet steal the warm chair right after you get up. Suddenly go on wild-eyed crazy rampage where is my slave? I'm getting hungry yet has closed eyes but still sees you

Mmmmmmmmmeeeeeeeeooooooooowwwwwwww curl into a furry donut kick up litter mmmmmmmmmeeeeeeeeooooooooowwwwwwww, and sit on human i am the best whatever.
